des: No longer do you need to wonder if it's a No Burn Day in the SF Bay Area - just ask! Works with every city in the Bay Area. This skill is not affiliated with the Bay Area Air Quality Management District and uses publicly available information from http://sparetheair.org website.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
